transcript:
Customer: السلام علیکم
Agent: Wa Alaikum Assalam, mein Ahmed bol raha hoon UBL se. Aap ki madad kese kar sakta hoon?
Agent: Alhamdulillah, main theek hoon. Aap sunaiye, aap kaise hain? Mein aap ki kis cheez mein madad kar sakta hoon?
Agent: Zaroor. Barah-e-karam apna TPIN batayen, chaar alag alag digits mein.
Customer: احمد مجھے اپنی بیلنس انکوائری کرنی ہے
Agent: Shukriya. Ab verification ke liye apna account number batayen.
Customer: 1 1 2 2
Customer: 1246789
Agent: Aap ka account balance 25,000 rupees hai. Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Customer: احمد یہ اکاؤنٹ نمبر تو میں نے غلط بتایا تھا یاں
Agent: Theek hai, barah-e-karam dobara apna account number batayen, take verification sahi se ho jaye.
Agent: Maazrat, verification ghalat ho gayi hai. Ab humein TPIN se dobara shuru karna hoga. Barah-e-karam apna TPIN chaar alag alag digits mein batayen.
Customer: 1 1 2 2
Agent: Shukriya. Ab dobara apna account number batayen, taake hum verification poori kar saken.
Agent: Aap ka account balance 15,000 rupees hai. Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
